   1:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c **** /**
   2:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   ******************************************************************************
   3:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   * @file    stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c
   4:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   * @author  MCD Application Team
   5:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   * @brief   LPTIM HAL module driver.
   6:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   *          This file provides firmware functions to manage the following
   7:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   *          functionalities of the Low Power Timer (LPTIM) peripheral:
   8:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   *           + Initialization and de-initialization functions.
   9:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   *           + Start/Stop operation functions in polling mode.
  10:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   *           + Start/Stop operation functions in interrupt mode.
  11:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   *           + Reading operation functions.
  12:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   *           + Peripheral State functions.
  13:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_lptim.c ****   *
